dcterms:description: Traffic data (flow, occupancy, speed) recorded using vehicle detector sensors (VDS) along the freeways and ramps. Raw data sampled at 30 second intervals are aggregated every 5 minutes. Flow data for one year (i.e., 104942 samples) from VDS 1114805 on California Interstate-05 NB in District 11 were used for training and testing of the models.
